description: Lists and describes insights for the specified insight ARNs.

parameters.name: InsightArns
parameters.description: The ARNs of the insights to describe. If you don't provide any insight ARNs, then GetInsights returns all of your custom insights. It does not return any managed insights. (string) ---

parameters.name: NextToken
parameters.description: The token that is required for pagination. On your first call to the GetInsights operation, set the value of this parameter to NULL. For subsequent calls to the operation, to continue listing data, set the value of this parameter to the value returned from the previous response.
